$. Finally, the\nthird regime is Boltzmannian (with $q=1$), and corresponds to short-range\ninteractions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Oct 2018 11:02:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 Jan 2019 14:12:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-09"}
